rg.com/s/c/IgJvilHUM50n_lAz5Dr0IfCVZNniMSZcaDu_BZx4rUB7MrWR3Jt7Gq3NoWdEWopyl9_9cfbES4rWF77BiZHSSojuv6gB8IA_U4_9RffluUVe1ZvKZUB1iByvIsLqMH1F6CHXxKO6O2NaIuPHglD-Y18xoz_B8N_XVOPo7KV4qbcI5qOJgmrHCp4GwUocuStJ978z2U9SeOhlbavRWad0eghDqBvC437RG3mb8-YC8zM3id90lQwthE3dJXWbdtCSWp8pj-LUxHCiM9P2BhJFjp9Zd6hsPH7if03jnDcpjAVTUaMPUP-2PBXfaUe89ro3UCooVcUtAFOuV6ojEndODfaRcwMi1NfkOAziRefYVK1ZDCNcWVmM4IUZCFc/R5hsLoeYfHaTr7rbq4BoQ2C2wdoABSiB/8" target="_blank"&gt;在五月中旬对加利福尼亚的豁免进行投票&lt;/a&gt;，尽管这可能首先需要参议院议员的决定 - 立法机构的首席规则守护者 - 首先。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/U2fes9yvK5ccEKAqcH9aemuyTPJFYWP1XzB8OXtuX0RxgR2Vck-SAofFLUw0oFc8cv1P3Q7qLjt0PmJZ_4ggvfo9KHqEw3N4xg0-y0APcLh17rAhME_bOKjZhzcyBCIIwpxVsAuFjmKBTNwyX0VwntyotH688DpRQ4zvXC-E0eQ8_WHjYxULlPM7vR4AsB9FcevKr63sL7SLUysctk805K5i2JRCYu2n5YRkj4Ki_fx6-j49UHabnAyabKrEatLyKxEG8GfN5oTAXEKEHydgWfo_Auh4hMSRbwkbA-4icKK0-361kLnEMyet-ravXuOGdbwvNssjtHuLN5S8adQeN5f-szWH0umaMjD6b5kpvq71iUYdUELI9FNJfxg/ref2bJiRKvoAmH4WE1dWbik1gIGY2gS_/8" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieohailZHmB4/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieohailZHmB4/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;交通沿着加利福尼亚州埃默里维尔市80号州际公路移动。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：David Paul Morris/彭博&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普捍卫大石油，因为各州声称气候伤害&lt;/strong&gt;。政府起诉阻止纽约和其他三个州&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/iZqrMAULW8sJ9mughGO-R_Nfh-Dj1iyiHe3TbMtUJP2_IwI4djsA5eAfeAGaqdF0ga66c9sd0wH54aEM49bnwdPBhaRbnsvvUHQVjCKAyuBsM5KMMVw2l5I9UKy6WaidSoky_1-7MMUt3w1mkrPwpxj-3IdaFMXkhLS8Giq5nyp4IVGjJ2U0DhHxwquOFJcBNgBU65cfIh11VuQb0mXvBoCiQwRl2VMj_OtQuZjBYs7PMtmmkak3xvt_I8PY8PIlGfH-Wbrq9xft2HCv9QjS-l8uQshgnAKkguMRcLRbcH-GElw80NZjrieiGTo8X-otIl1htPgVB2ds2ouMqOtvewbpSpBHJ9ThItGi9ywBWr0nmoEfixd-wdCYilY/gWMP3oQHQ25P8BHaS0hLg1iI9IZ0Uxbl/8" target="_blank"&gt;试图从石油公司收取数十亿美元，&lt;/a&gt;以造成气候变化造成的损害。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;投资者将汇丰银行宣布以寻求气候的答案。&lt;/strong&gt;一组30家汇丰控股公司PLC投资者要求该银行确认它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Be5VaYwNSm7N2yjHKmhRsi7zFaXEANiZlSYz6Tde-bYh-MFOlqbdvkR91OdNZTlkVNa1mdDoQ1Wtgb0aGyy2b6sRzL18H92iukzMmv4M34JChbP2M6WA8mZtib8fXbRZMuFmIG2JDfZFEXR-SuACZBi6PsbB4S4jYSNZEpI4G0VTYJa7_8mPdk9oXy_Z3qdI9TIDnv9YX1WIeKhtrN9vC9KMJBS2lBLm-9yhI03jHqFR-dwUYaRFZg-5FnXwOrVPax513sfCkoUhz7ejAWVNn5zpawLhX0VPmf4lgvDFKCed44umtBrF8Lam3ODH7X79LTg9ybAiCkJJq4HlwlhG4r8-RgYgb1bvDmknusiCfpx9ncCkDo9K-JT7ph8/IMEWr0eVI9n17czbcEmU0KT6LoPgwn0S/8" target="_blank"&gt;仍致力于减少二氧化碳排放&lt;/a&gt;，这是因为担心欧洲最大的贷方正在退出其气候承诺。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;气候适应是大生意&lt;/strong&gt;。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ufR5XI7F5HIxphTDZVZI0dE2ED-sPjXws1XV9RNBc9tv8uNIJpuCWXmnBcGUSdRZ_NOhvmoUy1gZOtLXvQN2paMN5ZTIoH_P01ZQYWXSpZfwgOAsFVcBjB2Sg-uHU4yHHQ5ks2oW8rcDgHWi5-g9NEnwBUwOMEYhQPLohiFOQZZuHmnWt4zThq3gHYlMea1AyXbeeQEb1QQYAyWN2zTU1h96jj1fERSvQ6IQhLdLRPAZSVgGjNmykaJiXJLli2TNr2RN6rsry-K4zi22fTzjrdMKKxQG6TNkZai_Gxk0uWOkDASi51aFBjvvBFaVu83II-NFRVMHNHmm16uvPiZFEekTNktdzvJF1VzDj4TC5wl8K7YfN8NLZXAztYM/k8sgHfHIS-ZA5wBUHvzIWrfzuICgfw_j/8" target="_blank"&gt;一份新报告称&lt;/a&gt;，到2050年，气候适应产生的收入可能达到4万亿美元，并为从消防技术到洪水保险提供投资机会。同时，风险投资公司Norrsken VC表示，欧洲需要对对气候友好的初创公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GFry7QbxfcounEZbXrFQvh5-Bfw_gq3rKn__G8YCRKaehzempRbh2ibtHwe9MW