巨额投资回报。这是因为新的担忧，即政府将需要&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/OZsYvw0YZ-USLo7rPTAhBgsx0SNB2uOYPtzCxrhXsB8c38VWOKdHbqXm9wUQgvEWggnFw58KqY5fh_HiwwPzb7cAoPBKdnvPlwBXJzzpkya3lJxyWobXC7s6Gkw3CLAzJiLy-rumNEDHHhOAaqKmnajPRnQQ1O1qoMWwtG_MmHMs-o31H9F4OEOfPq0SJjuATrtlgYEXT98_dBrFkAAxl2iorKnfk4_fPQ1smmAJcMpmOXmG5YUCR3ND9VlM7Wk-8w4E5yjty7MSBCF1xOwtLawoTKBTYJ1XkUJthGJbNyaf5A2sOMzPNLisQ4vWopA-icY4ssjexIv0Cd46sg-b8qEZi3uJeHY78OVGMW-GAqgBba7Igut8bpMNFQ/P7QpO79gtm7cYp892t79RHfA7SzJswlH/8" target="_blank"&gt;控制气候计划的支出&lt;/a&gt;，以履行&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/L5OzyfLMr67fodum0msLJrs2GV0T1jheDGYWsr0cs3EyfHIaxh7ghEVy32d0MzecJ6hoeU8rfhURQKo-fpHPRABX_HzRK4mK5tAZqzube3qA_OdsDpG-OIBPfFR7Cs88vqJcdqM7ikLBriAGRZJXVkxJf6rGV4_o3cEPEphIn8AMWb-gUS44CVUd29o21pNFzBdK_ciFSfiOb-kC3Hqy1TSXRYNXmPPga3TSSUeKnp3FoQrews1-43vVJKvFOg_J_bG3gIt8j_up95Vc-eBersfGxOWkDSBwVdR513QZOu6H0ptSm13L2l_AB0vrh9XQ80V1p8feArsYv6J5VORWkj9BQHuMoo8bKTZwHz9DVEaOOQh0r4zOSsjSuQ/MhbX8nYHsHooJqM7Ir6qUBwwR1KT7qTJ/8" target="_blank"&gt;诸如国防等&lt;/a&gt;新义务。&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;您还可以在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Iyfxh2syIMUQVZFCOi3GEPdO1SmkjbLru02NV_jBPxwiSaVclGvfsT7xmoLqDlmDBKllYsraxeZtCKIqwtL7du5vM4VZWv9oTDy5Lw0jLpnJsaK_jK5mHqpY1T2uuvQElQFkpFvPB3tqT8UPPHnPRCTbsxmu_ZYCaok1pp5M9WBBFiTY5bHnEpBssNL1PT1AktFiMB4L2glblAa6rGZotgn1qTpPmFvVLvc6gMwDL9cnysOBFcy7_BNhMa0PNi2JqfVchEW0ak6Hz6Xb08rLuOvoAOl5O0cXgnT38XV9XdySJ0fW2nveg3BSGAvm4t7ej5_jHqkx_cQ19f6XQ6XXh_rAaK86qELtgIb3T9Hrg7cHGwh8rAWDaH8nxw/FizWA3AWQc2klZFfwmuwsDmltit72yu3/8" target="_blank"&gt;彭博社&lt;/a&gt;上阅读&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xOYBvG5cAsgxvB2xUHqzyJWmS9Eq_lQSM1UIrQID7gK0AzTCEvQr8sFCe6MFnJMJFtEUWk2MgZ_fOqIEUTjEPyvOdT8NaAyvZ8J79Mym2UdoI2fHHnxi0J8rhNwwcTwyXwtmPYUqA6s21hazmDDrnjFmJFOFSJ6RK-wT1wbUy-l2dEQFy2hGqvV37wZ009wB4CHwOpesU0RQqOwak9wKAZRFnsfnwTA7N0fGB6qXe-Gn3ib4b4FyAiEe9pEUh_hd6dk_KbsSpGgK1EpRnU8Z8rXPpOtAztG0a7DW5h2Y6J-fAUJsFAf6SNvy